The predefined constant Zero represents integer 0 and is not suitable for
comparison with decimal values. The application should define a custom constant
for decimal zero, deriving it from Constant<Decimal> as the following code
shows.

public class decimal_0 : Constant<Decimal>
{
    public decimal_0()
        : base(0m)
    {
    }
}

...
// Using the constant in BQL.
public PXSelect<Table1,
    Where<Table.decimalField, Greater<decimal_0>>> records;

