Below is an example of a data view with CrossJoin and the corresponding SQL query.
PXSelectJoin<Table1, CrossJoin<Table2>> records;
SELECT * FROM Table1 CROSS JOIN Table2

Below is an example of a data view with InnerJoin and the corresponding SQL query.
PXSelectJoin<Table1, InnerJoin<Table2, On<Table2.field2, Equal<Table1.field1>>>> records;
SELECT * FROM Table1 INNER JOIN Table2 ON Table2.Field2 = Table1.Field1

Below is an example of a data view with LeftJoin and the corresponding SQL query.
PXSelectJoin<Table1, LeftJoin<Table2, On<Table2.field2, Equal<Table1.field1>>>> records;
SELECT * FROM Table1 LEFT JOIN Table2 ON Table2.Field2 = Table1.Field1

Below is an example of a data view with RightJoin and the corresponding SQL query.
PXSelectJoin<Table1, RightJoin<Table2, On<Table2.field2, Equal<Table1.field1>>>> records;
SELECT * FROM Table1 RIGHT JOIN Table2 ON Table2.Field2 = Table1.Field1

Below is an example of a data view with FullJoin and the corresponding SQL query.
PXSelectJoin<Table1, FullJoin<Table2, On<Table2.field2, Equal<Table1.field1>>>> records;
SELECT * FROM Table1 FULL JOIN Table2 ON Table2.Field2 = Table1.Field1

Below is an example of a data view with CrossJoin and the corresponding SQL query.
PXSelectJoin<Table1, CrossJoin<Table2>, InnerJoin<Table3, On<Table3.field3, Equal<Table1.field4>>>>> records;
SELECT * FROM Table1 CROSS JOIN Table2 INNER JOIN Table3 ON Table3.Field3 = Table1.Field4

Below is an example of a data view with InnerJoin and the corresponding SQL query.
PXSelectJoin<Table1, InnerJoin<Table2, On<Table2.field2, Equal<Table1.field1>>, LeftJoin<Table3, On<Table3.field3, Equal<Table1.field4>>>>> records;
SELECT * FROM Table1 INNER JOIN Table2 ON Table2.Field2 = Table1.Field1 LEFT JOIN Table3 ON Table3.Field3 = Table1.Field4

Below is an example of a data view with LeftJoin and the corresponding SQL query.
PXSelectJoin<Table1, LeftJoin<Table2, On<Table2.field2, Equal<Table1.field1>>, InnerJoin<Table3, On<Table3.field3, Equal<Table1.field4>>>>> records;
SELECT * FROM Table1 LEFT JOIN Table2 ON Table2.Field2 = Table1.Field1 INNER JOIN Table3 ON Table3.Field3 = Table1.Field4

Below is an example of a data view with RightJoin and the corresponding SQL query.
PXSelectJoin<Table1, RightJoin<Table2, On<Table2.field2, Equal<Table1.field1>>, InnerJoin<Table3, On<Table3.field3, Equal<Table1.field4>>>>> records;
SELECT * FROM Table1 RIGHT JOIN Table2 ON Table2.Field2 = Table1.Field1 INNER JOIN Table3 ON Table3.Field3 = Table1.Field4

Below is an example of a data view with FullJoin and the corresponding SQL query.
