The code below shows a data view and the corresponding SQL query.
PXSelect<Table1, Where2<Where<Table1.field2, Greater<Table1.field1> Or<Table1.field3, Equal<True>>>, And<Where<Table1.field3, IsNull, Or<Table1.field1, Equal<Table1.field2>>>>> records;
SELECT * FROM Table1 WHERE ( Table1.Field2 > Table1.Field1 OR Table.Field3 = 1 ) AND ( Table.Field3 IS NULL OR Table1.Field1 = Table1.Field2 )

An example of a data view and the corresponding SQL query are given below.
PXSelect<Table1, Where<Table1.field1, Equal<Table1.field2>>> records;
SELECT * FROM Table1 WHERE Table1.Field1 = Table1.Field2

An example of a data view and the corresponding SQL query are given below.
PXSelect<Table1, Where<Table1.field1, Greater<Table1.field2>, And<Table1.field3, IsNull>>> records;
SELECT * FROM Table1 WHERE Table1.Field1 > Table1.Field2 AND Table.Field3 IS NULL

